info.description:
CTypes-based python bindings to the GSASL library (www.gnu.org/software/gsasl).
This package provides a parser that generates python code w/ types checking and more pythonish feel
than just plain usage of the library through ctypes.
info.name: python-gsasl
info.summary: CTypes python wrapper for libgsasl library
